  <text>You unleash a blast of light and wind in a 15-foot Cone. Your allies in the Cone regain 2d6 Hit Points. Undead within the Cone that are Hostile to you must make a Constitution saving throw, taking 2d6 Radiant damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</text>
